{"description":"Pavil is a fellow Giga Chad on Abstract ecosystem whose art is what caught everyone's eye. 

He creates the most epic street art with web3 culture embedded in them. 

Seems like a good and helpful person in general as well. Top giga chad material for sure."}

{
  "description": "Red is super well-known as core community member on Green chain. His Giga chad badge says it more then any of my words. Been like a balm for my ears to hear his thoughts about getting Giga Chad role, that never focus on it personally, he is using all advantages on portal, like streaming, trading, gaming, collecting"
}

{
  "description": "",
  "source": "ethos-mobile"
}

{
  "description": "Pavil been one of the first Penguins I met on the timeline and only can say great things about him. 

His street art is so good really like the way he does those graffitis is just incredible and always showing up to support the penguins.

Definitly someone great to have in your circle."
}

{
  "description": "Zorin is one of those people you can have the funniest conversations with and also excels at what he does. He's absolutely nailed his personal brand and has worked alongside some of the top teams in web3. He's kind and patient and I LOVE watching him on streams."
}

{
  "description": "One of the very best artists for cutesy style art out there in the space and probably the world. Artist of the lovely chubbicorns. Very unique style, memelord. OG GIF make in this space! Have been frens with him since 2021. Can vouch for his skills and intergrity!"
}

{
  "description": "Aiz is a rare breed. I met him initially via his excellent infographics and was lucky enough to meet again through Gigaverse, where he champions growth and rallies the community and creators together. Not only is he extremely skilled in his fields, he manages to be so whilst remaining humble, patient and kind. He creates value and adds it to every room he's in, simultaneously. \n\nA true pleasure to know him."
}

{
  "description": "So grateful to have met WW through Cambria/Abstract. He's a fabulous creator and always a pleasure to talk to or play games with. He's skilled in the space but also a really great and genuine person."
}

{
  "description": "Lily Forest is an amazing and positive Abstract gigachad - one of the earliest contributors and a true vibe-maker in the community. She’s also a super fun and energetic streamer on the Portal. Every time I’ve joined her streams, the energy was incredible, she makes you feel part of something special!"
}

{
  "description": "MIC is one of the kindest and most supportive members of the Abstract community. As an OG Abstract member and the creator of the Vietnamese Abstract community, he’s played a huge role in growing and strengthening our ecosystem. Always helpful, positive, and dedicated - MIC truly represents what community spirit means!"
}

{
  "description": "PapaSmooth is one of the most trusted and valuable members of the Abstract community. He’s a genuinely great person with an incredibly positive attitude. I’ve known him for a long time, and he’s always been supportive, kind, and uplifting. Never seen anything bad from him — only good vibes and dedication!"
}

{
  "description": "When people talk to me about Loko, I think of the Ozy NFT collection. Loko is an abstract OG, he works and helps differents projects with his designer talents. In addition to being talented, Loko is extremely kind. Very happy to be by his side as a giga."
}

{
  "description": "I know him as giga chad in Abstract . A guy have a lot of powerfull in abstract community

What I like about this guy is his positivity about Abstract he shares on X, and his daring to speak the truth.

Will keep follow him in Abstract Journey."
}

{
  "description": "WhitestWizard is undeniably a pure person. I met him on abstract and he is a great person. He has always been involved in abstract, he is part of a team that builds on abstract, he is also a very good streamer. Always there to animate and please his community. WhitestWizard is a sensitive person, if you understand him he will become your best friend. It took me a while to understand him, and I realize that we don't see many people like him anymore. I wish you all the best."
}
